---
import ArticleLayout from '../layouts/ArticleLayout.astro';
---

<ArticleLayout
  title="Concierge | Wavey Dynamics"
  heading="WAVEY DYNAMICS CONCIERGE"
  subheading="Bringing motorsport technology to your driveway."
  image="/images/pages/concierge-hero-gt2.png"
  imagePosition="center 50%"
  description="Bespoke performance development for supercar owners. Motorsport-grade suspension, aerodynamics and data engineering applied to your car by Wavey Dynamics."
>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Modern high-performance cars are engineered to do everything well – long-distance comfort, daily usability, and track capability. But at the limit, compromise remains.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Even the most focused road cars are softened to suit a broad customer base. For our clients, that's not acceptable.</p>

  <p class="mb-10 leading-relaxed">Wavey Dynamics Concierge exists for those who want the undiluted version; a car defined by precision, not compromise.</p>

  <figure class="mb-12">
    <img src="/images/pages/concierge-road.png" alt="High-performance car — Wavey Dynamics Concierge"
      class="w-full object-cover" style="max-width:480px;display:block;margin:0 auto;" />
  </figure>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Who It's For</h2>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed"><strong>Wavey Dynamics Concierge</strong> is for high-performance road and supercar owners seeking a true 1 of 1, a track focused evolution of their car.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">For drivers who demand absolute purity and who are willing to go beyond the constraints of road car compromise to achieve it.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Whether the objective is circuit specific suspension development for Nürburgring Nordschleife, Spa-Francorchamps or maximising aerodynamic performance for high speed grip at your home circuits.</p>

  <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">That is the brief.</p>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">What We Deliver</h2>

  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start mb-12">
    <div class="flex-1">
      <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Our experience spans Hypercar development for clients such as McLaren, from clean-sheet concepts to the optimisation of established platforms such as GT3.</p>

      <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">This underpins our delivery of bespoke, performance-driven design solutions for high-performance road cars.</p>

      <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Our approach applies proven motorsport R&amp;D methods across the following areas:</p>

      <ul class="wd-list space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
        <li>Mass reduction
          <ul class="wd-list-2 mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
            <li>Suspension
              <ul class="wd-list-3 mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
                <li>Springs &amp; dampers</li>
                <li>Geometry</li>
                <li>Kinematics</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>Braking systems</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>Aerodynamics
          <ul class="wd-list-2 mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
            <li>Wings, splitters, flow devices, underbody aero</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>Powertrain tuning</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full md:w-[260px] shrink-0">
      <img src="/images/pages/concierge-supercar.jpg" alt="High-performance supercar"
        class="w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">How We Do It</h2>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">In motorsport, performance is defined by data. Interpreted correctly, it reveals the underlying physics and defines a clear path to measurable improvement.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed"><strong>Wavey Dynamics Concierge</strong> applies proven motorsport tools and development methodologies to extract meaningful insight and translate it into targeted, effective solutions.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Tools include:</p>

  <ul class="wd-list mb-10 space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
    <li>4-post suspension shaker rigs</li>
    <li>Wind tunnel and aerodynamic testing facilities</li>
    <li>Computational Fluid Dynamics (CFD) software</li>
    <li>Vehicle dynamics simulation software</li>
    <li>Data gathering instrumentation</li>
  </ul>

  <figure class="mb-12">
    <img src="/images/pages/concierge-rig.jpg" alt="Car on 4-post shaker rig"
      class="w-full object-cover" style="aspect-ratio:16/7;object-position:center 50%;" />
  </figure>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">The Concierge Experience</h2>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Define your objective. We define the path and manage the process end to end.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">On completion, you receive:</p>

  <ul class="wd-list mb-10 space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
    <li>A precisely developed machine, engineered using current motorsport R&amp;D methods to deliver uncompromised performance.</li>
    <li>A detailed engineering report, including before-and-after data analysis.</li>
    <li>Trackside support to refine setup and align the car with your driving style.</li>
    <li>Development documentation and behind-the-scenes insight.</li>
    <li>A driving experience defined entirely around you.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">The process is structured to keep you central, from initial definition through to final calibration.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Your car is developed as an extension of how you drive.</p>

  <p class="mb-10 leading-relaxed">Shaped by your objectives, refined through our engineering.</p>

  <figure class="my-10">
    <img src="/images/pages/concierge-journey.png" alt="Wavey Dynamics Concierge customer journey"
      class="max-w-[850px] w-full" />
    <figcaption class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-500">Wavey Dynamics Concierge — Bringing motorsport technology to your driveway.</figcaption>
  </figure>

  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-8">
    <a href="/contact" class="inline-block border border-(--color-border) px-6 py-2 text-sm no-underline hover:border-(--color-accent) hover:text-(--color-accent) transition-colors">Get in Touch →</a>
    <a href="/concierge-brochure.pdf" download="Wavey Dynamics Concierge Brochure 260620.pdf" class="inline-block border border-(--color-border) px-6 py-2 text-sm no-underline hover:border-(--color-accent) hover:text-(--color-accent) transition-colors">Download the Wavey Dynamics Concierge Brochure</a>
  </div>

</ArticleLayout>
